    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In the context of graffiti, bombing denotes prolific and repeated renderings of a single 'tag' in a given physical area in order to attract recognition.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
